ctxDrawImage(_0x348438,_0x34b63a,_0x511a4e,_0x4ce61b,_0x5cb03b,_0x1e6ff9,_0x2e28d4,_0x44271b,_0x23a4be,_0x176f2e){Settings['Xray']['e']&&(_0x348438['globalAlpha']=Settings['Xray']['o']);;if(_0x34b63a['tryLoad']===undefined||_0x34b63a['tryLoad']()===0x1){if(_0x176f2e!==undefined)_0x348438['drawImage'](_0x34b63a,_0x511a4e,_0x4ce61b,Math['max'](0x1,_0x5cb03b),Math['max'](0x1,_0x1e6ff9),_0x2e28d4,_0x44271b,_0x23a4be,_0x176f2e);else{if(_0x1e6ff9!==undefined)_0x348438['drawImage'](_0x34b63a,_0x511a4e,_0x4ce61b,_0x5cb03b,_0x1e6ff9);else _0x348438['drawImage'](_0x34b63a,_0x511a4e,_0x4ce61b);}}}function draw_info_box(){var _0x2e1432=game['info_box'],_0xc5de13=_0x2e1432['id'];if(_0x2e1432['activated']===0x1&&_0x2e1432['display']===0x1){if(INFO_BOX[_0xc5de13]===undefined)INFO_BOX[_0xc5de13]=create_info_box(_0xc5de13);if(_0x2e1432['craft']===0x1)ctxDrawImage(ctx,INFO_BOX[_0xc5de13],_0x2e1432['x'],_0x2e1432['y']);else{if(_0x2e1432['x']-0x50+INFO_BOX[_0xc5de13]['width']>canw)ctxDrawImage(ctx,INFO_BOX[_0xc5de13],canw-INFO_BOX[_0xc5de13]['width']-0xa,_0x2e1432['y']-INFO_BOX[_0xc5de13]['height']-0xa);else
